reportData.title: SQL query for C21_SCAN_REF
reportData.contents:
with transactions_for_more_tran_one_account as ( 
select top 1000 
tr.check_scan_transaction_id, tr.organization_unit_no, tr.check_scan_transaction_status_cd, 
count(distinct acc.account_Id) as accounts_count 
from check_scan_transaction as tr 
join check_scan_transaction_account as acc on acc.check_scan_transaction_id = tr.check_scan_transaction_id 
where 
--B = unit is branch 
organization_unit_type_cd = 'B' 
--branchNo 
and tr.organization_unit_no = 4454 
and (tr.check_scan_transaction_type_code is null or tr.check_scan_transaction_type_code !='PLAN_DEPOSIT') 
and tr.check_scan_transaction_status_cd = 'Scanned' 
group by tr.check_scan_transaction_id, tr.organization_unit_no, tr.check_scan_transaction_status_cd 
having count(distinct acc.account_Id)>1) 
select distinct account_id 
from check_scan_transaction_account as acc 
join transactions_for_more_tran_one_account on transactions_for_more_tran_one_account.check_scan_transaction_id = acc.check_scan_transaction_id
